rasterFunctionInfos.name: Analytic Renderer
rasterFunctionInfos.description: Chlorophyll A concentration in Log 10 scale at the ocean surface. The applied color ramp does not affect pixel values and therefore is appropriate to use in raster analysis.

rasterFunctionInfos.name: Cartographic Renderer
rasterFunctionInfos.description: Chlorophyll A concentration from low to high with an intuitive color-blind safe palette suitable for most applications. This renderer affects pixel value and should not be used for raster analysis.
